      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖拔出金刀，割了两块五寸见方的船帆，用刀尖在布上划了",
