      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "手一松，身子已与大船分离。那船行驶正快，向前一冲，洪七公已抓住小艇的船边，翻身入艇，悄无声息，等到郭靖也入艇来，说道：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有难",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 517
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有难",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖呢？你把他怎么了？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "火，火！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖一呆，忙道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公道：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖见大船上火盛，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 551,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 553,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖应道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 555,
      "line_end": 555
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洪七公骂道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 561,
      "line_end": 561
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈一笑，说道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 587,
      "line_end": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拉住船舷旁垂下的铁链，借力跃起，又上了甲板。洪七公道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 593,
      "line_end": 593
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓉儿，你瞧那西毒好凶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 597
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉仍不答。郭靖转过头来，见欧阳克正抓住她手腕，心中大怒，喝道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 601,
      "line_end": 601
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "灵蛇拳",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 611,
      "line_end": 611
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快去帮师父！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
